  "summary": "Apache Airflow is a distributed workflow orchestration platform consisting of multiple core components: a FastAPI-based REST API server, a Scheduler service, a DAG Processor, a Triggerer for async task handling, and pluggable Executors (Local, Celery, Kubernetes, etc.). The system uses SQLAlchemy for data persistence, supports multiple message brokers and result backends for distributed execution, and includes a web UI with role-based access control.",
